## Third-Party Licenses

This software incorporates third-party components with their own licenses:

### AI Model Integration
- OpenAI GPT-4o: Subject to OpenAI's Terms of Service and Usage Policies
- Anthropic Claude: Subject to Anthropic's Terms of Service

### Dependencies
- Node.js ecosystem packages: Various open source licenses (see package.json files)
- Chrome/Chromium: BSD-style license for PDF generation

### Fonts and Assets
- System fonts used in PDF generation retain their respective licenses
- Template designs are released under this MIT license

## Usage Guidelines

### Personal and CV Data
- This software is designed to handle personal information (CV/resume data)
- Users are responsible for their own data privacy and security
- No personal data is transmitted to external services without explicit user action
- Generated PDFs and documents contain user-provided information only

### AI Services
- AI features require API keys from supported providers (OpenAI, Anthropic)
- Users are responsible for their own API usage and associated costs
- AI-generated content should be reviewed before professional use
- Rate limiting and usage policies of AI providers apply

### Commercial Use
- Commercial use is permitted under this MIT license
- Attribution to original authors is appreciated but not required
- No warranty is provided for commercial applications

## Data Privacy Notice

This software:
- Processes CV/resume data locally by default
- Only sends data to AI services when explicitly requested by user
- Does not collect telemetry or analytics data
- Stores data locally in user-controlled files
- Users retain full ownership of their CV data and generated content

For questions about licensing or usage, please contact the maintainers.